                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6353" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1620</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8652 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成也萧何，败也萧何：海航多元化之殇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Success and failure: the war of HNA&#39;s diversification</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵青华，官钰芹，唐瑞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航集团；多元化；并购整合；财务困境</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HNA Group; Specialization; Merger and integration; Financial distress</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航借助政策东风成立以来，其成长之路可谓是一波三折，多次与“死神”擦肩而过。为了能够保持稳定的发展，海航高层决定实施产融结合的多元化发展战略，打造以航空上下游相关产业为主的并购链条。伊始，海航的确品尝到了“甜头”，而在“一带一路”倡议的提出后，海航则开始了一场停不下来的多元化扩张之旅。由于海航扩张速度过快、并购规模过大，公司出现了整合难，杠杆高等问题。随着去杠杆政策的实施，海航最终陷入债务深渊。本案例描述了海航自成立到最后破产重整的整个历程，追溯了海航的多元化扩张之路，阐述了海航盲目扩张后出现的种种问题。案例旨在引导学员了解海航进行多元化扩张的动因，关注多元化战略带来的风险，同时也希望能为上市公司提供借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the establishment of HNA with the help of policy Dongfeng, its growth path has been twists and turns, and it has missed the &quot;God of death&quot; for many times. In order to maintain stable development, HNA executives decided to implement the diversified development strategy of combining industry and finance and build an M &amp; a chain focusing on aviation upstream and downstream related industries. At the beginning, HNA did taste the &quot;sweetness&quot;, and after the &quot;the Belt and Road&quot; initiative was put forward, HNA began a non-stop diversified expansion journey. Due to the rapid expansion of HNA and the large scale of M &amp; A, the company has the problems of difficult integration and high leverage. With the implementation of the deleveraging policy, HNA finally fell into the abyss of debt. This case describes the whole process of HNA from its establishment to the final bankruptcy reorganization, traces the diversified expansion road of HNA, and expounds various problems after HNA&#39;s blind expansion. The case aims to guide students to understand the motivation of HNA&#39;s diversified expansion, pay attention to the risks brought by the diversification strategy, and hope to provide reference for listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业多元化战略的含义、多元化战略动因、所处环境分析等；采用多元化战略的好处和风险；企业多元化快速扩张后的整合问题、多元化并购后的协同效应；企业财务困境产生原因、盲目多元扩张的后果</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
